<br>
Sit - mob turns. Stand - mob turns towards tank. Rinse and repeat til mob no longer turns on you (tank has full aggro). It is just a matter of toggling your sit/stand key. 4 cycles is my record - 2 is average.<br>
<br>
Fun because while you are doing this, mob is not hitting tank at all - because of the shift target delay.<br>
